TITLE: Creating Initial Model in LikeC4
DESCRIPTION: Defines the top-level elements of the architecture model, including a customer actor and a SaaS system.
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/apps/docs/src/content/docs/tutorial.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: likec4
CODE:
```
specification {
  element actor
  element system
}

model {
  customer = actor 'Customer'
  saas = system 'Our SaaS'
}
```

