TITLE: Basic LikeC4 File Structure with Top-Level Statements
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the fundamental structure of a LikeC4 file with all possible top-level statements: specification (defines element kinds), model (architecture elements), views (visualizations), and global (shared predicates).
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/apps/docs/src/content/docs/dsl/intro.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: likec4
CODE:
```
// example.c4
specification {
  //...
}

global {
  //...
}

model {
  //...  
}

views {
  //...
}
```

