TITLE: Global Styles Configuration in LikeC4
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to define and apply global styles across different views, with the ability to mute elements and apply specific color schemes
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-21_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: zig
CODE:
```
global {
  style mute_all * {
    color muted
    opacity 10%
  }
}

views {
  view of app {  
    global style mute_all
    style cloud.* {
      color green
    }
  }  
}
```

