TITLE: Creating Auto-Layouts in Views - LikeC4
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to apply an auto-layout feature in views, arranging elements within a defined structure based on specified directions and distance parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/apps/docs/src/content/docs/dsl/views.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: likec4
CODE:
```
