TITLE: Basic View Definition in LikeC4
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to define named and unnamed views in the views section. Named views can be referenced and are used for file naming and URLs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/apps/docs/src/content/docs/dsl/views.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: likec4
CODE:
```
