TITLE: Creating Basic Relationships in LikeC4
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a simple relationship between two elements using the '->' operator in LikeC4.
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/apps/docs/src/content/docs/dsl/relationships.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: likec4
CODE:
```
model {
  customer = actor 'Customer'
  cloud = service 'Cloud'

  customer -> cloud
}
```

