TITLE: Adding Relationships Between Components in LikeC4
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to add a relationship between components within the same service. It demonstrates referencing elements within the same scope.
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/apps/docs/src/content/docs/dsl/references.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: likec4
CODE:
```
