TITLE: Filtering Relationships by Tag or Kind in LikeC4 DSL
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the 'where' clause to filter relationships based on source or target properties such as tags and element kinds. This enables creating more focused views that highlight specific aspects of the architecture.
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-21_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: zig
CODE:
```
include
  // only relationships outgoing from elements with with tag #next
  cloud.* -> amazon.*
    where source.tag is #next,

  // only incoming relations of elements with kind microservice
  -> *
    where target.kind is microservice
```

