SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-21_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: zig
CODE:
```
global {
  predicateGroup new_cloud_service {
    include cloud.*
      where kind is microservice
    exclude *
      where tag is #deprecated
  }
}
views {
  view of newServices {
    include *
    global predicate new_cloud_service
  }
  view of newBackendServices {
    include *
    global predicate new_cloud_service
  }
}
```

