TITLE: Implementing LikeC4View React Component
DESCRIPTION: Implements the main LikeC4View component that renders a LikeC4 diagram based on the provided viewId. It validates the viewId, conditionally injects styles, and passes properties to the underlying LikeC4Diagram component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/packages/likec4/src/cli/codegen/npm-package/index-template.txt#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: TSX
CODE:
```
export function LikeC4View({
   viewId,
   injectStyles = true,
   ...props
}: LikeC4ViewProps) {
  const view = LikeC4Views[viewId]
  if (!view) {
    throw new Error(`Invalid viewId: ${viewId}`)
  }
  return <>
    {injectStyles === true && <InjectStyles/>}
    <LikeC4Diagram view={view} {...props} />
  </>
}
```

