TITLE: Defining System Context View in Structurizr DSL
DESCRIPTION: Creates a system context view for the Internet Banking System, including all elements, defining an animation sequence, and setting properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/likec4/likec4/blob/main/apps/docs/src/content/docs/examples/bigbank.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: structurizr
CODE:
```
views {
  systemcontext internetBankingSystem "SystemContext" {
    include *
    animation {
      internetBankingSystem
      customer
      mainframe
      email
    }
    autoLayout
    description "The system context diagram for the Internet Banking System."
    properties {
      structurizr.groups false
    }
  }
}
```

